  <div class="inner">
    <h2 class="heading">AI writes code blind</h2>
    <p class="body">
      Your AI agent can search code without truly understanding how the system works. It misses that auth flows through three files, that the data model changed last quarter, or that the utility it needs already exists. ChunkHound gives every agent grounded, cross-file understanding of your codebase — so it can research before it edits.
